{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_31112.jpg","bgm":"bgm05_event07","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"...As soon as Kagome finished writing her record,","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"we returned to the Ark, huh."},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"I wonder where she and Torte are..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":831700},{"effect":"fadeout","id":402901}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_31112.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_31112.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"posY":80}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":831303},{"effect":"fadeout","id":810000},{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"They're here!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Ah...Mister Nicolas and Miss Perenelle."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"...I've noticed two things.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"What is it, Mother?"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"One is that, Torte, in your eyes..."},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"You have the power to bring back memories of@La Pucelle."},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"What?!"},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"When you made eye contact with those soldiers@earlier,"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"some kind of magic was triggered."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"Could it be because Torte's appearance closely@resembles La Pucelle,"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"and that acts as a magical catalyst for memories to@resurface...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"Perhaps that's how it works...@And the other thing is..."},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"When Kagome uses that pen"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"to record La Pucelle's memories,"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"It seems she can bring us back here from the world@in someone's mind."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":402901,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Huh... Is that so?"},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":0}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51158_tower_tart2/51158_kagome_magical_pencil.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"Yes, that pen possesses special magical power."},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"I sense the same magic from the recorded books..."},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"By writing with this magical pen,@it becomes a magical record, it seems."},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"I can't remember where I bought this..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"So is it...a magic mechanical pencil?"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story02","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51158_tower_tart2/51158_kagome_magical_pencil.png","visible":"hide"}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"Torte brings back memories of La Pucelle,"},{"chara":[{"id":831700},{"id":102001,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"And Kagome records their stories with that pen..."},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"Could repeating these two actions have a@meaningful purpose"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"in gathering La Pucelle's memories?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"We still don't fully understand the nature of this@space."},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"But the fact that Torte first encountered Kagome"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"might be the result of some mysterious force at@work."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810000,"pos":2,"posX":50}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"You might be connected to Tart through causality."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"It's not impossible."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Miss Jeanne...and us?"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"...What do you mean?"},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"pos":2,"posX":50}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"I don't know either."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"...Anyway, we can only try the same thing we did@before."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Yeah... But which book should we enter next?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Let's go back to where the books are!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_31111.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Torte","textCenter":"Hurry, hurry! Kagome!","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":831303,"pos":0}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":300,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Huff...huff...@Finally caught up."},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Let's go inside this big book! It'll be the third one!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Sure, but let's wait for everyone to catch up, okay?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":831303}],"flashEffect":"explosion","se":"3205_charm","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Huh...? Torte?!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.5,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001}],"flashEffect":"explosion","se":"3205_charm","textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_31111.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[